{
  "stem": "22728.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, I was a very angry person for a long time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I kept it well hidden.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had a lot of fun.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Our kids grew up just fine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we took up a hobby, family hobby.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went sailing all together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They all became sailors.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And competition weekends with like-minded couples-- we shared nothing but the sport in common.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My past was my private zone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I kept it to myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You can make choices like that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Maybe it was wrong.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Didn't?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, now?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, it started with my number two son, who is incredibly Jewish-minded.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He would rather live in Israel than anyplace else, and he is very active in UJA, and he is involved.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He lived on a kibbutz, Kibbutz Eilot for a year and has lots of friends in Israel.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when he heard about this, he says, Mom, why don't you consider telling what you have to tell?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, well, it's been a long time, and I don't remember enough.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, still, they may be able to use it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then if there are archives, if there's anyone looking for you, just think of that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So, at first it didn't appeal to me at all.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He said, here, take this number.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Call it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So I did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And what did she tell me?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My goodness, we got 10,000 phone calls.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I wasn't exactly unique.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But at first it drove me crazy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to bed, and I took a nap.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think I was ready.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And now it's been a few months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Time has gone by.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't mind.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] There were years, much longer ago, when this would have been more than difficult for me because of the memories.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
